lojban gismu foo

 * allgismu - assuming make and perl are installed, generate "all"
   potential (legal) gismu via

     make depend
     make all

   otherwise study the graph in the 'graph' file, as parsed and executed
   by the code in 'allgismu'

 * badgismu - generates every possible five letter word composed of
   legal Lojban consonants or vowels. some of these are legal gismu

 * similar-gismu searches the ../lefanva generated dictionary file for
   similar gismu
